    "The objective is to guarantee that the generated scenarios are plausible and adhere to the provided framework.",
    "They found that including elements inspired by fiction into LLMs improves creativity and imagination in the scenario development process.Koide et al. [46] present a strategy for detecting phishing websites using LLMs.",
